--> Create user account:- 
step.1 -> setup mongoose
step.2 -> setup schema
step.3 -> setup model
step.4 -> usercreate
step.5 -> encrypt(hash) password
step.6 -> create jwt token
step.7 -> set the token as a cookie on the browser

--> jab user login karega toh fir token receive hoga server side par and then uss token ko decrypt karenge toh fir email-id milegi
    or uss email-id ko match karenge toh fir true aayega toh login hoga else nahin hoga